core04=1\n\n|RD5-team01={{flagIOCathlete|[[Oliver Taylor (boxer)|Oliver Taylor]]|AUS|1960 Summer}}\n|RD5-score01=0\n|RD5-team02='''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Primo Zamparini]]|ITA|1960 Summer}}'''\n|RD5-score02='''5'''\n}}\n\n===Finals===\n\n{{Round4\n|RD1 = Semifinals\n|RD2 = Final\n| team-width=250\n| score-width=20\n<!--Date-Place|Team 1|Score 1|Team 2|Score 2 -->\n<!--semi finals -->\n||'''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Oleg Grigoryev]]|URS|1960 Summer}}'''|'''4'''|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Brunon Bendig]]|POL|1960 Summer}}|1\n||{{flagIOCathlete|[[Oliver Taylor (boxer)|Oliver Taylor]]|AUS|1960 Summer}}|0|'''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Primo Zamparini]]|ITA|1960 Summer}}'''|'''5'''\n<!--final -->\n||'''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Oleg Grigoryev]]|URS|1960 Summer}}'''|'''3'''|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Primo Zamparini]]|ITA|1960 Summer}}|2}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Footer Olympic Champions Boxing Bantamweight}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Boxing At The 1960 Summer Olympics - Bantamweight}}\n[[Category:Boxing at the 1960 Summer Olympics|Bantamweight]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Olympic boxing tournament}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2018}}\n{{Infobox Olympic event\n|event = Bantamweight boxing\n|games = 1960 Summer\n|image = \n|caption = \n|venue = [[PalaLottomatica|Palazzo dello Sport]]\n|dates = 25 August \u2013 5 September\n|competitors = 32\n|nations = 32\n|gold = [[Oleg Grigoryev]]\n|goldNOC = URS\n|silver = [[Primo Zamparini]]\n|silverNOC = ITA\n|bronze = [[Brunon Bendig]]\n|bronzeNOC = POL\n|bronze2 = [[Oliver Taylor (boxer)|Oliver Taylor]]\n|bronzeNOC2 = AUS\n|prev=[[Boxing at the 1956 Summer Olympics \u2013 Bantamweight|1956]]\n|next=[[Boxing at the 1964 Summer Olympics \u2013 Bantamweight|1964]]\n}}\n{{Boxing at the 1960 Summer Olympics}}\nThe '''men's bantamweight''' event was part of the [[Boxing at the 1960 Summer Olympics|boxing programme]] at the [[1960 Summer Olympics]].  The weight class allowed boxers of up to 54 kilograms to compete. The competition was held from 25 August to 5 September 1960. 32 boxers from 32 nations competed.<ref name=\"SR\">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1960/BOX/mens-bantamweight.html |title=Boxing at the 1960 Rome Summer Games: Men's Bantamweight |work=Sports Reference |accessdate=25 November 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Competition format==\n\nThe competition was a straight single-elimination tournament, with no bronze medal match (two bronze medals were awarded, one to each semifinal loser). There were 33 boxers entered, but the boxer from the [[Republic of China (Formosa) at the 1960 Summer Olympics|Republic of China]] withdrew at the last minute, too late to change the bracket; therefore, one bout was conducted in the round of 64 and one boxer received a bye in the round of 32.\n\n==Results==\n[[File:Oliver Taylor, Brunon Bendig, Oleg Grigoryev, Primo Zamparini 1960.jpg |thumb|Left-right: Oliver Taylor, Brunon Bendig, Oleg Grigoryev, Primo Zamparini]]\n\nResults of the bantamweight boxing competition.<ref name=\"SR\"/><ref name=OR691to98>Official Report, pp. 691\u201398.</ref>\n\n===Top half===\n\n{{16TeamBracket-Compact-NoSeeds-Byes\n|RD1=Round of 32\n|RD2=Round of 16\n|RD3=Quarterfinals\n|RD4=Semifinals\n\n| team-width=195\n| score-width=40\n\n|RD1-team01='''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Thein Myint]]|MYA|1960 Summer}}'''\n|RD1-score01='''5'''\n|RD1-team02={{flagIOCathlete|[[Charles Reiff]]|LUX|1960 Summer}}\n|RD1-score02=0\n\n|RD1-team03={{flagIOCathlete|[[Sadegh Ali Akbarzadeh Khoi]]|IRI|1960 Summer}}\n|RD1-score03=1\n|RD1-team04='''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Muhammad Nasir]]|PAK|1960 Summer}}'''\n|RD1-score04='''4'''\n\n|RD1-team05={{flagIOCathlete|[[Waldomiro Pinto]]|BRA|1960 Summer}}\n|RD1-score05=0\n|RD1-team06='''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Oleg Grigoryev]]|URS|1960 Summer}}'''\n|RD1-score06='''5'''\n\n|RD1-team07='''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Frankie Taylor]]|GBR|1960 Summer}}'''\n|RD1-score07='''KO-1'''\n|RD1-team08={{flagIOCathlete|[[Paavo Roininen]]|FIN|1960 Summer}}\n|RD1-score08=L\n\n|RD1-team09=\n|RD1-score09=\n|RD1-